OL,5,G1500 Castle
OL,6,     FBeckett has her faith tested when
OL,7,     Fshe investigates the murder of an
OL,8,     Festate agent and all of the
OL,9,     Fevidence points to Castle.
OL,10,G1555 Castle
OL,11,     FBeckett and Castle teleport in to
OL,12,     Fa sci-fi convention to investigate
OL,13,     Fthe murder of the fan of a
OL,14,     Fcancelled TV show.
OL,15,G1650 Love Nature
OL,16,     FIn Brighton we meet growers at an
OL,17,     Fallotment who offer their produce
OL,18,     Fto local food banks. The charity
OL,19,     FNurture through Nature is staffed
OL,20,     Fby volunteers, for whom gardening
OL,21,     Fis a release.
