OL,5,G2000 Draining Loch Ness
OL,6,     FThe plug is pulled on the famous
OL,7,     Floch, using comparisons with the
OL,8,     Fdeepest lake on earth, combined
OL,9,     Fwith military-grade scanning tech
OL,10,     Fand a sonar curtain across its
OL,11,     Fsurface.
OL,12,G2100 Milan with Michael Portillo
OL,13,     FIn Italy's capital of fashion,
OL,14,     Fdesign and industry, Michael races
OL,15,     Ffast cars, see the sites from the
OL,16,     Fback of a 1960s Lambretta and
OL,17,     Flearns the skills of Italian
OL,18,     Fcoffee making.
